The lori costume basically makes one of your enemies attack another one.

e.g. a 2 dino (yours) vs 2 dino fight (winks & softpig). If one of your dinos uses the lori costume one of the opponents will carry out one attack on him own dinos. i.e. the winks would attack the softpig. From what I have seen this attack is with the dinoz main element.

Hope that helps
